### API Gateway Tests - Port 8080

### 1. Register User (via Gateway - No Auth)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Gateway",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "gateway@gaadix.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "phone": "9876543210"
}

### 2. Login User (via Gateway - No Auth)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "gateway@gaadix.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 3. Search Vehicles (via Gateway - No Auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/search/vehicles?brand=Maruti&minPrice=300000&maxPrice=800000

### 4. Get Vehicle by ID (via Gateway - Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/vehicles/1
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 5. Get Pricing Estimate (via Gateway - No Auth)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/pricing/estimate?vehicleId=1

### 6. Create Payment (via Gateway - Auth Required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "vehicleId": 1,
  "buyerId": 1,
  "amount": 550000,
  "paymentMethod": "UPI"
}

### 7. Verify RTO (via Gateway - Auth Required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/rto/verify
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "registrationNumber": "MH12AB1234",
  "vehicleId": 1
}

### 8. Get Dashboard Analytics (via Gateway - Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/analytics/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

### 9. Check Fraud Risk (via Gateway - Auth Required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/fraud/check
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "vehicleId": 1,
  "sellerId": 2,
  "buyerId": 1,
  "transactionAmount": 550000
}

### 10. Send Notification (via Gateway - Auth Required)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/notifications/send
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_ACCESS_TOKEN

{
  "userId": 1,
  "type": "EMAIL",
  "notificationType": "PAYMENT_SUCCESS",
  "subject": "Payment Successful",
  "message": "Your payment of ₹550000 was successful"
}
